author: Freddie Clayton
description: Israeli Defense Minister Israel Katz has vowed to block an aid vessel carrying Greta Thunberg and other activists from reaching Gaza, by “any means necessary.”The "Madleen" departed Sicily last Sunday, aiming to breach Israel's naval blockade on Gaza, deliver humanitarian aid, and draw attention to the worsening humanitarian crisis in the enclave
title: Israel vows to stop aid boat carrying Greta Thunberg from reaching Gaza
